        <p class="aerys-hero__tag">Clinical Sleep Optimization &middot; Medical-Grade &middot; USA</p>

        <h1 id="hero-headline" class="aerys-hero__headline">
          You Wake Up Exhausted Every Morning.<br><br>
          <span class="hi">Even After 8 Hours of Sleep.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="aerys-hero__sub">
          It&rsquo;s not a sleep problem.<br><br>
          It&rsquo;s an oxygen problem.<br><br>
          Every night your mouth stays open,<br>
          your body loses oxygen &mdash; and your sleep never fully recovers.
        </p>

        <p class="aerys-hero__sub">
          And every night this continues,<br>
          your recovery gets worse.
        </p>

        <p class="aerys-hero__sub">
          AERYS&trade; fixes that.<br>
          From the very first night.
        </p>

        <p class="aerys-hero__sub">
          Fix your sleep starting at just $1 per night.<br>
          One small strip. Massive difference.
        </p>

        <p class="aerys-hero__social-proof">🚀 Free U.S. Shipping &mdash; Arrives in 3&ndash;5 Days</p>

        <div class="aerys-hero__cta-row">
          <a href="#bundles" class="btn btn-brand">Fix Your Sleep Tonight &rarr;</a>
          <a href="#bundles" class="btn btn-ghost">Try It Risk-Free for 30 Nights</a>
        </div>

        <p class="aerys-hero__social-proof">⭐ 4.9/5 from 2,847+ verified users</p>

        <div class="aerys-hero__trust" aria-label="Trust signals">
          <span class="aerys-hero__trust-item">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            Medical-Grade Silicone
          </span>
          <span class="aerys-hero__trust-item">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            HSA / FSA Eligible
          </span>
          <span class="aerys-hero__trust-item">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            30-Night Money-Back Guarantee
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="aerys-hero__body" aria-label="About AERYS">
          <div class="aerys-hero__stanza" aria-label="How AERYS works">
            <span>One strip.</span>
            <span>Applied in seconds.</span>
            <span>Every night.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- ── Right: Product visual (image-first) ── -->
      <div class="aerys-hero__media" aria-label="AERYS™ sleep strip">

        <img
          class="aerys-hero__img-product"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0808/8112/3545/files/product-main.png?v=1776730988"
          alt="AERYS™ medical-grade mouth tape — the strip you apply before sleep"
          width="600"
          height="600"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
        >

        <!-- Rating badge -->
        <div class="aerys-hero__media-badge" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
          <span>4.9 &mdash; 2,847 reviews</span>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
